// RUSSIAN GAME - 56%
1. e4 e5 2. Nc3 Nf6 3. Nf3

    // 66%
    3... Nc6 4. Bb5 - see four knights, spanish 

    ==============================================================================================
    ==============================================================================================
    // RUSSIAN GAME, REVERSED SPANISH - 20% 
    // the lines I've chosen in this variation look very cool and dynamic 
    3... Bb4 4. Nxe5 

        ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
        ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
        4... O-O 5. Nd3             // +0.17
        
            --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
            // played in almost all games 
            5... Bxc3 6. dxc3          // 98% 

                ----------------------------------------
                6... Nxe4 7. Nf4            // +0.16 - Be2 scores +0.17 but Nf4 has a higher winrate at 2200

                ----------------------------------------
                6... Re8 7. f3              // +0.35

            ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
            ~5... Ba5 6. e5           // 1.1%, +0.47 
        
        ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
        ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
        4... Bxc3 5. dxc3           // +0.23 

        ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
        ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
        4... Qe7 5. Nf3             // +0.49 - I prefer Nf3 here because there are good followups - high winrates and interesting positions

            --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
            5... Bxc3 6. dxc3       // take with the right pawn

            --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
            5... Nxe4 6. Nd5        // attack the queen 

        ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
        ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
        4... d6 5. Nd3              // +0.25 - Nf3 scores better engine wise, but Nd3 is more forcing and has a higher winrate
                                    // Nf3 also isn't as interesting here. And Nd3 is similar to the main line, might even transpose

    ==============================================================================================
    ==============================================================================================
    // RUSSIAN GAME, FLAWED ITALIAN - 5.6%
    // it's not a good move but it isn't completely lost, black can still apply some pressure, so you have to know the lines 

    #3... Bc5 4. Nxe5 

        ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
        ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
        // this is the variation you have to know, because black can apply alot of pressure if you don't play 6. h3 preventing Ng4. 
        // black has a high winrate, but once you play h3 white has a very high winrate
        
        4... Nc6 5. Nxc6 dxc6 6. h3                     // 73%, +0.83 

        ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
        ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
        4... O-O 5. d4                                  // 10.4%, +0.71 

            --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
            5... Bb6 6. ? 

            --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
            5... Bb4 6. ? 

        ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
        ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
        4... Qe7 5. d4                                   // 8%

            --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
            5... Bb4 6. ? 

            --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
            5... d6 6. ? 

            --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
            5... Bb6 6. ? 

            --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
            5... O-O 6. ? 

        ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
        ~4... d6 5. ?

        ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
        ~4... d5 5. ?

        ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
        ~4... Bd4 5. ?

    ==============================================================================================
    ==============================================================================================
    // PHILIDOR, NIMZOWITSCH VARIATION - 5.6%
    3... d6 4. d4 

        4... Nc6 5. Bb5 - transposes w/ four knights, spanish w/ 4... d6 5. d4 - 4% 

        ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
        ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
        // PHILIDOR, HANHAM, LION VARIATION 
        4... Nbd7 5. Rg1                                      // 85% - rare move at 2200 but powerful, good winrate 

        ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
        ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
        4... exd4 5. Nxd4                                      // 9.7%
